Citation.sTitle: Liquid-liquid equilibria for the ternary system water + decane + diethylene glycol monobutyl ether at 20 C, 30 C, and 40 C
Citation.sAbstract: Liquid-liquid equilibria measurement of a ternary system water + decane + diethylene glycol monobutyl ether at 20.0, 30.0, and 40.0 C were made at atmospheric pressure. The experimental data were correlated well with the UNIQUAC model.
